		<title>Mayo Clinic Q&amp;#038;A: How does a cancer diagnosis affect family building</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-qa-how-does-a-cancer-diagnosis-affect-family-building/</link>
		
